# Project Overview

## Task
AI Content Marketing using UGC Ads

## Product Chosen
Laneige Lip Sleeping Mask

## Objective
The objective of this project is to design a structured prompt engineering system that generates high-converting UGC-style ad content.

UGC ads are widely used because they:
- Feel authentic and relatable
- Build trust faster than traditional ads
- Drive higher engagement and conversions

This project demonstrates how AI can generate:
- Scroll-stopping hooks
- UGC ad scripts
- Conversion-focused CTAs
- Platform-ready captions

## Target Platform
Instagram Reels / Short-form video ads

## Core Problem
Many users struggle with dry, flaky lips and use ineffective lip balms that provide only temporary relief.

## Solution Approach
Using prompt engineering, we generate UGC-style ad content that highlights:
- Real user problems
- Transformation results
- Sensory product experience
- Social proof and relatability
